fields.description: Additional options directly passed to SQL DW in Copy Command. Type: key value pairs (value should be string type) (or Expression with resultType object). Example: "additionalOptions": { "MAXERRORS": "1000", "DATEFORMAT": "'ymd'" }
fields.name: AdditionalOptions

fields.description: Specifies the default values for each target column in SQL DW. The default values in the property overwrite the DEFAULT constraint set in the DB, and identity column cannot have a default value. Type: array of objects (or Expression with resultType array of objects).
fields.name: DefaultValues
